       <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-500" data-template-id="progress-label" style="color: rgb(113, 128, 150); font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-size: 16px;">Daily progress</span> <span id="progressText" class="text-sm font-semibold" style="color: rgb(107, 163, 214); font-weight: 700;" data-template-id="progress-text">0 of 0 completed</span>
      </div>
      <div class="h-3 overflow-hidden" style="background-color: #FFFFFF; border-radius: 9999px;">
